WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.220 --> 00:00:05.339
The Mailtraq webmail server installs as part
of Mailtraq Professional and allows Users

00:00:05.339 --> 00:00:09.250
to access their mail from anywhere in the
world using a standard web-browser (such as

00:00:09.250 --> 00:00:16.289
Internet Explorer, Firefox, Safari, Chrome
etc) or Internet enabled mobile device. The

00:00:16.289 --> 00:00:23.630
intuitive layouts, multiple language support,
anti-spam, spell-checking and extensive user

00:00:23.630 --> 00:00:31.179
Options make the Mailtraq webmail server the
natural choice for organizations of all sizes.

00:00:31.179 --> 00:00:45.360
The Mailtraq webmail server is easy
to set-up and a breeze to administer.

00:00:45.360 --> 00:00:46.930
The Mailtraq webmail server provides three
interfaces:

00:00:46.930 --> 00:00:51.150
EWA - Enhanced Web Access for IE6 and above
Standard - Cross-browser compatible for IE,

00:00:51.150 --> 00:00:55.980
Thunderbird, Opera, Mac-users etc
Mobile - 'Standard' for low bandwidth and

00:00:55.980 --> 00:00:59.020
mobile devices
Secure private webmail server

00:00:59.020 --> 00:01:03.470
The Mailtraq webmail server gives you the
convenience of web based email like Gmail™

00:01:03.470 --> 00:01:10.140
or HotMail™ while keeping control over your
own private data. Use webmail instead of installing

00:01:10.140 --> 00:01:14.260
mail clients on to each computer,and make
considerable savings for your business on

00:01:14.260 --> 00:01:20.630
your software and administration costs. Use
WebMail in schools and colleges to provide

00:01:20.630 --> 00:01:24.270
students with secure, monitored email.

00:01:24.270 --> 00:01:28.520
Mailtraq webmail provides a feature rich,
easy to use email system designed to be used

00:01:28.520 --> 00:01:34.591
as the primary email client in your organization.
It offers the full range of essential email

00:01:34.591 --> 00:01:38.890
services your users require without any additional
license costs - it even includes Secure Webmail.

00:01:38.890 --> 00:01:47.479
Mailtraq webmail connects you direct to your
existing email account providing a mobile

00:01:47.479 --> 00:01:53.840
extension of your real e-mail mailbox. You
can read, compose, forward, or reply to messages

00:01:53.840 --> 00:01:59.310
from your mobile device while maintaining
your normal, real existing email address and

00:01:59.310 --> 00:02:04.439
mailbox. You have direct access to all of
your folders on your mobile device, and the

00:02:04.439 --> 00:02:09.860
full webmail feature set can be applied from
your desktop, to control signatures and 'personas'.

